To contribute to elexis.info

# git://github.com/elexis/elexis.github.com.github
# make your changes
# sudo aptitude install ruby
# gem install bundler
# bundle install
# bundle exec rake webserver
# point your browser at http://127.0.0.1:4000/ and see whether everything is okay

Multilingual support (not yet implemented is documented here: https://www.klaasnotfound.com/2017/02/16/proper-multilingual-site-with-github-pages-and-jekyll/
